Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.25,0:01:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本以为结束了我都在笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.02,0:01:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖蒙和那个逸扎却又出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.88,0:01:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边正在为了让亚加玛离开殖民卫星而拼命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联系信号却很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.07,0:01:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人接近了亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z的状况也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.39,0:01:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果 我还是用了光束步枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第九话 宇宙的捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们殖民地香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.09,0:02:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙中看起来的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.73,0:02:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个玫瑰小子马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.15,0:02:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想让安多拉离开香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像那种怪人最让人头痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉比安罗兹到底在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核战机还没到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉比安罗兹的会合?地点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.44,0:03:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,都怪这里垃圾太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也是这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.54,0:03:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,附近没有动静吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看2加2...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,监视情况怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,没有异状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也到处是垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们认真点阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.06,0:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与在香格里拉时的态度\n完全不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗达,借给我啊\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是运动场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.57,0:03:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拿这个给舰长看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太大了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再小一点才能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.87,0:03:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再继续寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.81,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冠武,那不是玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,干什么的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可能迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷路她怎么不讲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那么倔强,不会讲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们自己来找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先找到的话\N露卡会生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没空去讨小孩的欢心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话是这样说没错...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇斯洛,用雷达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.68,0:04:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米诺夫斯基粒子浓度不高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好检定方位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让敌人发现我们\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多拉杰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不修理密达斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能飞就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花姊姊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个假陨石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险,退后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是假陨石?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会太小?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看,开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.24,0:05:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.81,0:05:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个放在宇宙中\N还会增加五十倍大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么大...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那MS不就可以躲在这个后面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假陨石\N不是只有陨石形状的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模仿殖民地残骸而做的假钢板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来是很小...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数量多的时候\N就可以用来隐藏亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.89,0:05:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装上炸弹也能成为气雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比米诺夫斯基粒子更好用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MS战时也能应用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.40,0:05:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么特雷斯你开密达斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗时不用假陨石?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要光使用武力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为当时是在殖民地内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对...对阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请来看房间分配图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分配房间?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么可以擅自决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.27,0:06:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别计较嘛\N又不可能顾到所有人的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的房间也得换吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个当然有考虑到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟学校一样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟学校一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来,伊诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.35,0:06:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆,来就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点发出强力电波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.74,0:06:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安多拉就能知道亚加玛的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.81,0:06:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出卖亚加玛太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等!你仔细想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再打下去我们又赢不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如把亚加玛卖给安多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.94,0:06:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回香格里拉更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要背叛亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不依赖大人才活下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.89,0:07:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别到宇宙就变了一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为捷杜会撑很久吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.13,0:07:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真以为他是新人类吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过过好日子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把亚加玛卖掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能买新MS了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后再捡破烂吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.72,0:07:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.82,0:07:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不适合再亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就到MS甲板上面去\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊莱,你再做什么??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现强力电波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.74,0:07:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!几秒就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是电波强的不寻常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亚加玛吗?确认位置了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是亚加玛的话\N就不太正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像故意告诉我们位置似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.69,0:08:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材,亚加玛内有内奸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦...\N我们与香格里拉市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.95,0:08:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和好相处的努力成果出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛内部有人支持亚古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着,马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.09,0:08:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有得到市民的信赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.87,0:08:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官才可能有好的表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你必须亲近市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与他们打成一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N这是身为领导者必须注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗?马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.06,0:08:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽量注意的,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内奸?真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给内奸看看亚古捷斯的诚意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用哈玛哈玛过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人一定会赞成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人\N请让我派人支援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那个必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.59,0:09:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的魄力与重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达根本不是对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有新型MS哈玛哈玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.38,0:09:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是究极的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有他在,我就必胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.71,0:09:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们一生最大的请求\N马士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我们\N帮马士文大人你的忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.62,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧,随便你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有一群好部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈玛哈玛,出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没到宇宙了\N心情也跟着雀跃起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等着吧,亚加玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于要开动MS实际作战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在东张西望什么东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉不住气的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.45,0:10:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连亚加玛都跟丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.76,0:10:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌!我叫他们要好好跟着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小孩吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬起头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪一个部队的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出所属舰名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所属舰名?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.91,0:11:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这...我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是突然被召集的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.59,0:11:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就被赶鸭子上架做飞行训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.04,0:11:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也不知道\N自己是在哪里飞行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是奥干的人\N还是联邦军的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的少女...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你带这位少女去安多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疑?马士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我初次上阵阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们新手驾驶员来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.30,0:11:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟生日一样可贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.06,0:11:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太啰唆了,敢不听命令吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.73,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么马士文大人对女人\N都这么溺爱呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.28,0:12:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位,我会想办法自己回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.25,0:12:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么客气话?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.48,0:12:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们亚古捷斯\N是各位市民的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明,别怠慢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不亏是地球圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然有让我ㄧ眼就迷上的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢你了,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祸不单行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法,只好顺着形势去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.60,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你说一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌人MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.12,0:13:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是上次的敌人,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不同MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.52,0:13:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入第一备战状态\NZ高达出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.66,0:13:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解,MS...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放出假陨石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布拉杜舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫捷度快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用之前用的大炮迎敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.05,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荧幕全打开  
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.35,0:13:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!我要跟你谈阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不穿太空衣你会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥,知道敌人的数目吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.43,0:13:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他可出动的MS呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.81,0:13:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你没立场说那种话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛的船员中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最擅长驾驶Z高达的人是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比花更厉害不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得倒是很简单阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给他Z高达的资料\N马上送他出阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的,捷度是新人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.92,0:14:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.44,0:14:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛被击沉,你也一样要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也没必要要我先死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.51,0:14:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是新人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.48,0:14:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你过去对Z高达\N的操作就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别拍马屁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会上当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你无处可去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.49,0:14:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想你住在亚加玛上面的同伴死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.80,0:14:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹也在阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N我关舱门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.05,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人有5架,好像更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候该说什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.04,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度.桑达,Z高达出动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度那小子\N忘记来福枪的能源盒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.39,0:15:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,我们去作战斗后食物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗达,冠武,来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才刚做完午餐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人没吃午饭吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能是空着肚子作战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.25,0:15:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以老是这么弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别挡着,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去找各位子坐吧\N是...是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多资料我看不完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是机器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次看这么多东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡怎样了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会是被敌人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,只有一架Z高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙,我只有一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了!明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.41,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙中我是不会手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有能源了...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记带能源盒阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来决斗吧,Z高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙中你就无处使力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗不只是用蛮力!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.23,0:16:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了!有假陨石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用来雷射来福枪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.88,0:16:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想逃走吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达没有雷射来福枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各机全力飞行直接把它围起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.64,0:17:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗时还这样松懈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.73,0:17:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的飞机,通讯系统没有坏阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么飞机?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小型飞机很少有这么\N好的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有机舱...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是装饰品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.41,0:17:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,是真的,可以用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以开枪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥干阵营有正式采用这个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.51,0:17:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.31,0:17:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里会被卷入战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地的爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要当好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.16,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡,你想回家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假陨石不知能不能撑的很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.84,0:18:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算跑到陨石群中\N你也逃不掉的,Z高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.96,0:18:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是假陨石,烦死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达,不要跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些气球太碍事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨克C队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.28,0:18:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别被假陨石骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直线前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你能一直用假陨石到何时?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们连真假陨石都分不清吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙连基本常识都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次毁3架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么只有1架?数目不对阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.72,0:19:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你用假陨石太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你5比1不是更卑鄙吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是1比1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没意见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时才公平决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我变的更讨厌你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡,那是敌人的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是Z高达吗?\N太好了,我真幸运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你带我过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨克C队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那战机\N根再香格里拉看到的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡\N你为什么攻击我又跑回来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,古利明,你没受伤吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么回来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.99,0:20:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若是受伤我会很为难的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.33,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为难?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你对我很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.93,0:20:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N我是站在亚加玛那边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.99,0:20:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡,马世文大人去追截你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了\N我好像快忘记自己的使命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.44,0:20:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先收拾你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了,力量下降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.71,0:20:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有穿太空衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想不战而逃吗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.17,0:21:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛里面有我们的同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.16,0:21:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的卑鄙的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会受到报应的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫名奇妙,跑来偷袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.64,0:21:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但什么是也不做就逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人总是有很多理由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.80,0:21:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来你可以击沉一架MS的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人真是的\N我是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且被抓去安多拉当人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我费了多少苦心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.61,0:21:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃离那里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是迷路而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.77,0:21:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然,我才没有那么笨阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁晓得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.30,0:21:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.72,0:22:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,敌人说亚加玛有他们的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.87,0:22:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那是随便讲讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.52,0:22:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.66,0:22:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是你听错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.44,0:22:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.58,0:22:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你们两位了,去休息吧\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.14,0:22:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长,是拉比安罗兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.05,0:22:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?靠近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.35,0:22:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它发现到我们了\N是的

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.37,0:23:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为拉比安玫瑰不能接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.34,0:23:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花拼死出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.58,0:23:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛内却出现了帮助马士文的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是露干得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.43,0:24:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从拉比安玫瑰运来了新型的战机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.33,0:24:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不能指望伪装陨石啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.07,0:24:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 高达ZZ 再见了，花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.73,0:24:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐真是可怜
